  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Category:</strong> Clan <br /><strong>Prerequisite:</strong> Leone Clan, level 8+ <br />As the head of your \"pride\" your steadfast presence fosters an extreme degree of teamwork very rarely seen in others. You gain the following benefits;</p><ul><li>Increase your Wisdom or Charisma by +1, to a maximum of 20.</li><li>As long as you and a packmate are within 20ft of one another and can see each other, you and those packmates are immune to the berserk, demoralized/fear and charmed conditions.</li><li><p>Whenever a packmate would be reduced to 0 hitpoints or killed, you and all packmates within 60ft may spend your reactions to do an action that would take either a Action or Bonus action. This may be triggered once per combat.</p></li><li>You cannot be forced to harm or betray your packmates or those that a packmate holds close as the result of a jutsu or feature that would normally cause you to act against your will.</li></ul>",
      "chat": ""
    },
